  "text": "This study highlights the need to broaden the understanding of training processes through the analysis of pedagogical variables that define a task. The integration of knowledge from the experience of expert coaches with empirical knowledge is basic to applied research [CITATION_1] . The results presented in this study provide a promising method for the integration of theoretical and practical knowledge, as well as promotion of this type of applied research to sports pedagogy.",
